## Configuration and Dependencies

- Python ≥ 3.8;
- `openai`, `tqdm`, `sentence-transformers`, `scikit-learn`, `nltk`, etc.—see the `dependencies` list in `pyproject.toml`.
- We recommend using the `uv` tool for a consistent experience.

